Purpose: Coding or technical help,Study scheduling or organization,Concept understanding,Other (please specify)
PurposeOther: Letting it review my work (feedback) based on a specific rubric
DescribeChange: Firstly, if I have a hard time grasping the assignment, I will ask it to formulate it in a different way with more context or just more words. Secondly, for creating papers/experiments, I use it to brainstorm effectively. I give it my current ideas and ask for elaboration or a different view point, which often enlightens me because I would not have thought about it in such away (also due to time constraints). If I am stuck I will also ask for an outline on an assignment, key words to find research materials, or just feedback on my current writing. All things that I didn't have access to before and likely enhance my writing now. For studying, I use it to summarize tough paragraphs or to get explanations in just the right depth with examples or mnemonics. This indeed enhances efficity of studying, but it still often makes mistakes, so I do not use it too heavily. However the availability of AI tools has most prominently changed how I work with it as a extensive feedback tool, for explanations, codes, and for schedule advice.
